            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "NPC Core pg. 40",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "NPC Core",
          "page": 40,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Most who end up in a jail, dungeon, or prison are just biding their time through the interminable days until their imprisonment ends. Some, however, use force and intimidation to gain status, and create makeshift weapons to take down their enemies or use in a jailbreak.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
